**Code Splitting & Lazy Loading:**
- Route-based code splitting for each main section (Dashboard, Marketplace, Wallet, Chat, Profile)
- Component-level lazy loading for heavy features (charts, file upload, admin panels)
- Progressive loading of tier-based features based on user status

**Real-time Performance:**
- WebSocket connection optimization with reconnection logic
- Debounced PXL rate updates to prevent excessive re-renders
- Chat message pagination to limit DOM size
